OL,3,CBed found for critically ill girl who
OL,4,Cneeds 'Berlin Heart'
OL,6,FA critically ill 14-month-old girl who
OL,7,Fwas facing a life threatening wait for
OL,8,Fa specialist NHS bed has been given a
OL,9,Fbreakthrough chance of survival after
OL,10,Fa huge fundraising campaign to help
OL,11,Fher.
OL,13,FPenelope Greathead, who has dilated
OL,14,Fcardiomyopathy, has been on life
OL,15,Fsupport at Leeds Children's Hospital
OL,16,Fafter suffering a cardiac arrest last
OL,17,Fmonth.
