OL,3,CBed found for critically ill girl who
OL,4,Cneeds 'Berlin Heart'
OL,6,FThe youngster, from Ravenscar near
OL,7,FScarborough, needs a device known as a
OL,8,FBerlin Heart to keep her alive long-
OL,9,Fterm until an organ donor can be found.
OL,11,FBut with a shortage of specialist beds
OL,12,Favailable to support the treatment -
OL,13,Fand with her life support machine
OL,14,Freaching the limit of its
OL,15,Feffectiveness - Penelope's loved ones
OL,16,Ffeared she may die before she could
OL,17,Fhave the procedure.
OL,19,FThey launched a bid to raise #120,000
OL,20,Fto pay privately for a Berlin Heart,
OL,21,Fpotentially to be fitted abroad.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
