OL,3,CBed found for critically ill girl who
OL,4,Cneeds 'Berlin Heart'
OL,6,FHowever, on Monday they received the
OL,7,Fnews that a space had become available
OL,8,Fat London's Great Ormond Street
OL,9,FHospital.
OL,11,FIn a post on Facebook, the family
OL,12,Fsaid: "This is the only the very
OL,13,Fbeginning of her journey but we now
OL,14,Fhave a plan and hope.
OL,16,F"Thank you so much to all the amazing
OL,17,Fstaff in Leeds Children's Hospital for
OL,18,Ftaking care of our baby."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
