OL,3,CBed found for critically ill girl who
OL,4,Cneeds 'Berlin Heart'
OL,6,FDespite being diagnosed with her heart
OL,7,Fcondition shortly after she was born,
OL,8,FPenelope was otherwise healthy until
OL,9,Fshe suffered a cardiac arrest during a
OL,10,Froutine medicine change.
OL,12,FStaff at Leeds Children's Hospital
OL,13,Fperformed 12 minutes of emergency
OL,14,Fresuscitation and she has been on life
OL,15,Fsupport since.
OL,17,FThe news that she will now be treated
OL,18,Fin London came after more than
OL,19,F#125,000 was raised in her honour from
OL,20,Fmore than 4,000 donations.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
