OL,3,CBed found for critically ill girl who
OL,4,Cneeds 'Berlin Heart'
OL,6,FThe money will now go to charity.
OL,8,FIn a post on the online fundraising
OL,9,Fpage, Penelope's dad Jordan Greathead
OL,10,Fsaid: "There are no words that can be
OL,11,Fused to say how thankful we are to
OL,12,Feach and every single person who has
OL,13,Fdonated, shared Penelope's story or
OL,14,Fsent us messages of support.
OL,16,F"We also want to use this outlet to
OL,17,Fexpress our gratitude to the staff at
OL,18,FLeeds Children's Hospital who have
OL,19,Fprovided the most amazing care to our
OL,20,Flittle girl over the last three weeks."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
