OL,3,CBed found for critically ill girl who
OL,4,Cneeds 'Berlin Heart'
OL,6,FIt is hoped Penelope will have her
OL,7,FBerlin Heart fitted by the end of the
OL,8,Fweek, which would allow her loved ones
OL,9,Fto have close contact with her again.
OL,11,FMum Holly Suff said: "Sometimes when
OL,12,Fher sedation isn't on point she puts
OL,13,Fher hands up for us to hold her and we
OL,14,Fcan't right now. So just being able to
OL,15,Fhold her - that will be unbelievable."
OL,17,FThe couple hope Penelope's story
OL,18,Fprompts more people to consider
OL,19,Fbecoming organ donors.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/7
